channel.title: No servers will work for me!
channel.description:
Okay, so i have recently downloaded Codyscape, and tried to run it and it said that Java wasn't reconginized.
So i went and downloaded the Java from java.com and The SDK java. (Which i was linked to when i tried to run the "runserver")
Does anyone know why i can't get any clients/servers to work?

item.title: No servers will work for me!
item.dc:creator: @IconsOfEvil IconsOfEvil
item.description:
@IconsOfEvil wrote:

I’ve got the problem fixed.

All i did was go into a computer, that played client with no problem, and get the cache.
I put it in a .rar file and sent it too my computer and extracted it where it needs to be, and now client works.

Only thing is, Clients don’t work.
